Mangope Mangope died last week at the age of 94. JOHANNESBURG - The memorial service for former Bophuthatswana Lucas Mangope is underway in his home village of Motswedi outside Zeerust in the North West. Mangope Mangope died last week at the age of 94. The former leader's funeral service takes place on Saturday in Motswedi. WATCH: Lucas Mangope memorial service 